      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，EMR同步触发初始化到Absent。那如果患者扫描'End'会怎么样？直接结束流程吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "End"
