    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不是的，扫描'End'从Absent状态会触发错误，这个错误由HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine处理，进入'Error'状态。另外CheckedIn之后扫描'End'才是正常的'Attended'状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "Error",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "End"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上了：Absent到Error的转移（DiagnosticEngine处理），以及CheckedIn到Attended的转移。现在CheckedIn如果重复扫描'Start'呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "CheckedIn状态下扫描'Start'会触发HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine，但状态保持CheckedIn，相当于重复签到提醒。Attended之后扫描任何操作都由HealthTech_EMR_Sync处理，状态保持Attended。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckedIn",
