      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：CheckedIn自循环（DiagnosticEngine），Attended自循环（EMR_Sync）。那Error状态能恢复吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Error",
